comments.body: sadly it's no longer a complete list of lookup plugins. Not sure how we want to handle things like this. Ideally, we'd say something like "a list of lookup plugins included in ansible-base see foo.  Also see the documentation for any installed collections that may also provide lookup plugins.

diffHunk:
@@ -1,1 +21,25 @@
For more details and a list of lookup plugins in ansible-base, see :ref:`plugins_lookup`. You may also find lookup plugins in collections. You can review a list of lookup plugins installed on your control machine with the command ``ansible-doc -l -t lookup``.

.. seealso::
